<h1>Start the Cluster</h1>
<p>
    <strong>Initiate the cluster instances.</strong>
</p>
<p>
In this step we request instances for the master, worker and Cassandra nodes.
</p>

<p>
The suggested price is a 50% margin over the last recorded price.
</p>

<div class="form-horizontal">
    <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-3 control-label" for="master_price">Master limit price</label>
        <div class="col-sm-9">
            <input id="master_price" class="form-control" type="text" name="master_price" aria-describedby="master_price_help">
            <span id="master_price_help" class="help-block">
                Specify a maximum price for the master instance.
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-3 control-label" for="worker_price">Worker limit price</label>
        <div class="col-sm-9">
            <input id="worker_price" class="form-control" type="text" name="worker_price" aria-describedby="worker_price_help">
            <span id="worker_price_help" class="help-block">
                Specify a maximum price for the worker instances.
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-3 control-label" for="workers">Number of workers</label>
        <div class="col-sm-9">
            <input id="workers" class="form-control" type="text" name="workers" aria-describedby="workers_help">
            <span id="workers_help" class="help-block">
                Specify the number of worker instances.
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-3 control-label" for="cassandra_price">Cassandra limit price</label>
        <div class="col-sm-9">
            <input id="cassandra_price" class="form-control" type="text" name="cassandra_price" aria-describedby="cassandra_price_help">
            <span id="cassandra_price_help" class="help-block">
                Specify a maximum price for the Cassandra instances.
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-3 control-label" for="cassandras">Number of Cassandra nodes</label>
        <div class="col-sm-9">
            <input id="cassandras" class="form-control" type="text" name="cassandras" aria-describedby="cassandras_help">
            <span id="cassandras_help" class="help-block">
                Specify the number of Cassandra instances.
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">
        <label class="col-sm-3 control-label" for="cassandra_seeds">Number of Cassandra seeds</label>
        <div class="col-sm-9">
            <input id="cassandra_seeds" class="form-control" type="text" name="cassandra_seeds" aria-describedby="cassandra_seeds_help">
            <span id="cassandra_seeds_help" class="help-block">
                Specify the number of Cassandra seeds (must be less than the number of Cassandra instances).
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button id="start_cluster" class="btn btn-default" type="button">Start cluster</button>
</div>
<p></p>
<p style="margin-top=20px;margin-bottom=20px;">
JSON Data
</p>
